Numstore
===============

Overview
--------
Numstore is a lightweight numerical array database and CLI toolset designed for high-performance numerical data storage and retrieval.

Features:

Installation
------------
To build and install Numstore

1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/lincketheo/numstore.git

2. Bootstrap the build system:
   ./autogen.sh

3. Configure the build:
   ./configure

4. Build the project:
   make

5. Install the binaries:
   sudo make install

